close_reason: replace-tests update workflow delivered and verified in remediation wave
body: "External report reproduced in this repository: pm update currently rejects --clear-tests combined with --test, forcing manual remove/add loops through pm test for each linked test entry. This task adds explicit replacement semantics while preserving deterministic validation and backward compatibility."
